  "title": "Senior Sales Engineer (Oil & Gas Sector)",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Senior Sales Engineer</strong></h2><h3><strong>Additional Information</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Up to S$4,000 + S$800 Transport Allowance + Commission + Bonus + AWS</p></li><li><p><strong>Working Location: </strong>Ubi Crescent</p></li><li><p><strong>Working Hours: </strong>5-day work week, 8:30am – 6:00pm</p></li><li><p><strong>Annual Leave: </strong>14 days</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Prospect and develop new customers while maintaining existing key accounts.</p></li><li><p>Prepare quotations for project tenders and provide technical support to customers.</p></li><li><p>Review technical documents and work closely with the Sales Manager.</p></li><li><p>Attend site meetings, provide after-sales support, and follow up with customers.</p></li><li><p>Build and maintain strong, long-term relationships with customers.</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>ITE or Diploma in Electrical / Electronics Engineering.</p></li><li><p>Minimum 2–3 years of sales experience, preferably with strong contacts in:</p><ul><li><p>Oil & Gas</p></li><li><p>Petrochemical</p></li><li><p>Utilities & Power Plant sectors</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Strong communication and presentation skills.</p></li><li><p>Proactive, results-oriented, and able to work independently.</p></li></ul>",
